{"about_the_game":"<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Overview</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">&quot;Spectrum of the Puddle&quot; is an exhilarating action game where water and light bounce around.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enemies appear on fixed 2D screens\u2014take them down one after another.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game consists of a total of four stages, each filled with hordes of enemies and a boss awaiting the protagonist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The protagonist's weapon may be just an ordinary umbrella, but in the world of puddles, it\u2019s a valiant hero\u2019s sword. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It can even fire lasers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302900/extras/player_run.gif?t=1738116113\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Game System</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In addition to regular attacks, you can dodge danger by guarding or jumping.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game features powerful &quot;skills&quot; and &quot;belongings&quot; that grant unique effects to the protagonist. You'll have opportunities to customize these during gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u30b9\u30c8\u30fc\u30ea\u30fc</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">&quot;A mysterious world where puddles stretch on endlessly.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">In the rain-washed sky, a rainbow lingered, never fading away.&quot;</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A lonely girl wandered into another world.<br>What will she encounter here, and what thoughts will fill her mind?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302900/extras/rainbow.png?t=1738116113\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">&quot;I wonder how many colors I\u2019d divide a rainbow into.&quot;</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Specter of the Puddle","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3302900/58c52768263817d9b46be434bb43ab6cbf8d6d1c.jpg"},{"name":"Spectacle of the Puddle","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3302900/b5bb13ccbfb620aaaee7625c84c210f2af2f1943.jpg"},{"name":"Spectrum of the Puddle","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3302900/72a22a3848b40defb94e9aee1b41b1fd49044677.jpg"}],"total":3},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302900/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738116113","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302900/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738116113","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302900/bd6e0c7f554b4ec6bd61eae5f8735e5d5973c265/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738116113","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302900/bd6e0c7f554b4ec6bd61eae5f8735e5d5973c265/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738116113","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Overview</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">&quot;Spectrum of the Puddle&quot; is an exhilarating action game where water and light bounce around.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enemies appear on fixed 2D screens\u2014take them down one after another.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game consists of a total of four stages, ea